I am thinking of a situation where the Building Bridges Initiative, courtesy of the Handshake, never happened as well. Seemingly, we would have made exceedingly large strides towards development.
My hypothesis is informed by the now common trend where almost every failure of the country is attributed to BBI. The narrative has persistently been repeated until the larger populace has come to believe that BBI is responsible for all the country’s woes.
The worst instance is when citizens are made to believe that BBI has largely hampered the war against Covid-19.



